## 📋 Connection Tables

### 1. Arduino Mega → L298N Motor Driver #1 (Front Motors)

| Arduino Pin | L298N #1 Pin | Description |
|-------------|--------------|-------------|
| D22 | IN1 | Front Left Motor Direction 1 |
| D23 | IN2 | Front Left Motor Direction 2 |
| D2 (PWM) | ENA | Front Left Motor Speed (PWM) |
| D24 | IN3 | Front Right Motor Direction 1 |
| D25 | IN4 | Front Right Motor Direction 2 |
| D3 (PWM) | ENB | Front Right Motor Speed (PWM) |
| GND | GND | Common Ground |
| 5V | 5V (Logic) | Logic level power |

### 2. Arduino Mega → L298N Motor Driver #2 (Back Motors)

| Arduino Pin | L298N #2 Pin | Description |
|-------------|--------------|-------------|
| D26 | IN1 | Back Left Motor Direction 1 |
| D27 | IN2 | Back Left Motor Direction 2 |
| D4 (PWM) | ENA | Back Left Motor Speed (PWM) |
| D28 | IN3 | Back Right Motor Direction 1 |
| D29 | IN4 | Back Right Motor Direction 2 |
| D5 (PWM) | ENB | Back Right Motor Speed (PWM) |
| GND | GND | Common Ground |
| 5V | 5V (Logic) | Logic level power |

### 3. Arduino Mega → NEO-6M GPS Module

| Arduino Pin | GPS Module Pin | Description |
|-------------|----------------|-------------|
| D10 | TX | GPS transmit → Arduino receive |
| D11 | RX | Arduino transmit → GPS receive |
| 5V | VCC | Power (from Buck Converter #2) |
| GND | GND | Ground |

### 4. Arduino Mega → HC-05 Bluetooth Module

| Arduino Pin | HC-05 Pin | Description |
|-------------|-----------|-------------|
| D18 (TX1) | RX | Arduino transmit → Bluetooth receive |
| D19 (RX1) | TX | Bluetooth transmit → Arduino receive |
| 5V | VCC | Power (from Buck Converter #2) |
| GND | GND | Ground |

**⚠️ IMPORTANT:** HC-05 RX is 3.3V logic. Use a voltage divider:
```
Arduino D18 (5V) ───[1kΩ resistor]───┬───► HC-05 RX
                                      │
                              [2kΩ resistor]
                                      │
                                     GND
This creates 3.3V from 5V signal.
```

### 5. L298N Motor Drivers → TT Motors

#### L298N #1 (Front Motors)
| L298N #1 Terminal | Motor Connection |
|-------------------|------------------|
| OUT1 | Front Left Motor (+) |
| OUT2 | Front Left Motor (-) |
| OUT3 | Front Right Motor (+) |
| OUT4 | Front Right Motor (-) |

#### L298N #2 (Back Motors)
| L298N #2 Terminal | Motor Connection |
|-------------------|------------------|
| OUT1 | Back Left Motor (+) |
| OUT2 | Back Left Motor (-) |
| OUT3 | Back Right Motor (+) |
| OUT4 | Back Right Motor (-) |

### 6. Power Connections

#### Battery → Motor Drivers
| Battery Terminal | Connection |
|------------------|------------|
| Positive (+) | Through Power Switch → L298N #1 +12V, L298N #2 +12V |
| Negative (-) | GND to both L298N modules |

#### Battery → Buck Converters → Arduino & Modules
| Component | Input | Output | Connected To |
|-----------|-------|--------|---------------|
| Buck Converter #1 | 7.4V from battery | 5V, 1A | Arduino Mega VIN, GND |
| Buck Converter #2 | 7.4V from battery | 5V, 0.5A | GPS VCC, Bluetooth VCC |

