## 🔍 Troubleshooting

| Problem | Possible Cause | Solution |
|---------|----------------|----------|
| Arduino doesn't power on | Buck converter not adjusted | Measure output, adjust to 5V |
| Motors don't spin | Wrong pin assignment | Double-check wiring vs code |
| Motors spin weakly | Low battery | Charge battery, check connections |
| GPS no fix | Indoors, bad antenna placement | Move outdoors, wait 60s |
| Bluetooth won't pair | HC-05 not powered | Check 5V and GND connections |
| HC-05 damaged after connecting | No voltage divider on RX | Replace HC-05, add voltage divider! |
| Robot turns when going straight | Motor speeds unequal | Calibrate speed in code |
| Robot drifts from waypoint | GPS accuracy limit | Normal, reduce WAYPOINT_THRESHOLD |

