| Connection Type | Wire Gauge | Notes |
|----------------|------------|--------|
| Battery → Drivers | 18-20 AWG | High current |
| Motor → Driver | 20-22 AWG | Moderate current |
| Power (5V) | 22-24 AWG | Low current |
| Signal (GPIO) | 26-28 AWG | Jumper wires OK |

